Description: Meta-package for necessary OpenBib infrastructure
 Build a search-portal (virtual OPAC) consisting of multiple catalogues
 using different (integrated) library systems. Currently several
 origin catalogues are supported: Sisis, Lidos, Filemaker, OAI among
 others. The meta-data format is German MAB2-oriented (Maschinelles
 Austauschformat fuer Bibliotheken) but the database-scheme isn't
 restricted to any special meta-data format, so a port to MARC21 is
 possible.

